snippet.title: Kit's Quest - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Kit’s Quest is a challenging, fun-filled 3D platformer featuring a brave fox on a journey to rescue his sister from a menacing dragon! Explore a huge, interconnected world, collect magical dragon teeth, and learn cool abilities as Kit treks towards Skyreach Summit to save the day!

Early Access release coming to Steam on January 6th!


Play Free Demo: https://lonefoxgames.itch.io/kits-quest
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2017840/Kits_Quest
Release News and More: https://www.KitsQuest.com/

© 2022 Lone Fox Games
